      <div class="msgContentFrame">Devastate is Prot's spammable filler ability, no CD (besides global 1.5), decent damage and threat, applies a stack of sunder armor.  Revenge is useable for a few seconds anytime you block, parry, or dodge an enemy's attack.  Revenge is higher damage and threat, but has a 5 sec CD.  What (I think) the OP wants is 1 button he can hit that will cast Revenge if it's available, Devastate the rest of the time.</div>
